(145, 1, '2015-12-14 20:32:37', '2015-12-14 20:32:37', '<h2><span style="color: #993366;">μισός και πλέον αιώνας ιστορίας</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #999999;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">Η  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">Ελληνική  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">Φωτογραφική  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">Εταιρεία,  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">μη  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">κερδοσκοπικός </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">οργανισμός,     </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">     </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">είναι     </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">το     </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">αρχαιότερο     </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">ερασιτεχνικό </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">φωτογραφικό  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">σωματείο  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">της  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">χώρας  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">μας.  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">Ιδρύθηκε  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">πριν </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">από  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">60  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">χρόνια  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">(Ιανουάριος  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">του  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">1952)  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">από  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">μια  </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">ομάδα </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">εγκρίτων   </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">Αθηναίων   </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">πολιτών,   </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">φανατικών   </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">φίλων   </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">της </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">φωτογραφίας,    </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">και    </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">για    </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">πολλά    </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">χρόνια    </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">υπήρξε    </span><span class="xr_tl xr_s11">ο </span><s